1
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:13,260
Oh no!

2
00:00:14,730 --> 00:00:16,630
How dare you bring bad luck on such a joyous day.

3
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:17,630
Do you want to die?

4
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:20,760
General Weibei is here for the wedding procession.

5
00:00:20,830 --> 00:00:22,200
So fast?

6
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:24,030
But the general entered the manor

7
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:26,530
and went straight to Ms. Shen's quarters in the servants' rooms.

8
00:00:26,530 --> 00:00:27,630
What?

9
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:28,400
Shen Lvyi

10
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,460
is just a lowly concubine without even a wedding dress.

11
00:00:30,460 --> 00:00:32,259
What kind of procession is this?

12
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:34,900
The Lu Army brought 288 boxes from the Internal Affairs Department.

13
00:00:34,900 --> 00:00:36,630
They said it's all Ms. Shen's dowry.

14
00:00:36,630 --> 00:00:38,060
It can't even fit in the manor.

15
00:00:38,060 --> 00:00:40,130
It's stacked all over the street outside.

16
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:43,060
All the commoners are watching and talking about it.

17
00:01:05,630 --> 00:01:07,060
The bride is so beautiful.

18
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:09,260
A match made in heaven.

19
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,960
Stop!

20
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,630
Shen Lvyi, have you no shame?

21
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:30,300
Lu Jingxing is my husband.

22
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:31,960
Madam's marriage was bestowed by His Majesty.

23
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,729
My marriage was also bestowed by His Majesty.

24
00:01:33,729 --> 00:01:34,759
Today is a joyous day.

25
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:36,030
With so many people watching,

26
00:01:36,030 --> 00:01:38,259
Madam should mind your manners,

27
00:01:38,259 --> 00:01:39,990
and not make a fool of yourself.

28
00:01:43,530 --> 00:01:45,060
Go away, do that over there.

29
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:47,860
You're blocking my view of my fairy lady.

30
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:49,060
Lu Jingxing!

31
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,229
I am your lawfully wedded wife.

32
00:01:51,229 --> 00:01:52,500
I am the primary and she is the secondary.

33
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,759
You should have come for me first.

34
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,700
That would be in accordance with etiquette.

35
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:56,860
Divorce paper?

36
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:59,160
You want me to write you a divorce paper?

37
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,360
Lu Zhong.

38
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,660
Bring pen and paper.

39
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:02,960
I was talking about etiquette.

40
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,330
Not a divorce paper.

41
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:07,030
Etiquette?

42
00:02:07,030 --> 00:02:09,729
According to etiquette, you are the primary and she is the secondary.

43
00:02:09,729 --> 00:02:11,400
Doesn't everything start from secondary to primary?

44
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,600
Just wait at home.

45
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,800
I'll give you a grand procession later.

46
00:02:46,829 --> 00:02:48,260
The newlyweds step over the fire.

47
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,700
May your years be prosperous.

48
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:50,860
General and Madam.

49
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:52,990
May you enjoy long life and happiness.

50
00:02:58,130 --> 00:02:59,130
Lvyi.

51
00:02:59,130 --> 00:03:00,130
Let me carry you.

52
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,400
I'll do it myself.

53
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,560
Great moves.

54
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,690
As expected of our general's beloved.

55
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:37,630
His Majesty has arrived!

56
00:03:44,829 --> 00:03:45,900
Rise.

57
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:48,200
I'm here for the wedding feast today.

58
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,260
Don't be so formal.

59
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:51,360
Jingxing and I

60
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,730
are monarch and subject in public.

61
00:03:52,730 --> 00:03:53,500
But in private,

62
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:56,500
we have a life-and-death bond forged in seas of blood.

63
00:03:58,230 --> 00:04:00,430
Thank you for gracing us, Your Majesty.

64
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:23,760
Oh no!

65
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:26,230
They are already performing the wedding ceremony at the Weibei General's manor.

66
00:04:26,230 --> 00:04:28,560
His Majesty even went to attend the feast.

67
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:31,960
Impossible.

68
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,730
This is impossible.

69
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:37,800
Shut up and don't cry.

70
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,300
Why are you wailing on a joyous day?

71
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:41,000
Our marriage was bestowed by His Majesty.

72
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,700
I don't believe Lu Jingxing would dare not come to marry you.

73
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,430
Right.

74
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:45,900
He wouldn't dare.

75
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,960
His Majesty wouldn't allow him to do so either.

76
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,100
Master and Madam.

77
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:51,960
The general has sent something to pick up the young lady.

78
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:55,159
I told you Lu Jingxing wouldn't dare skip the procession.

79
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,760
Has General Weibei entered?

80
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:57,730
Let him wait.

81
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:00,500
Let's make him anxious this time.

82
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,230
The general hasn't come.

83
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:03,030
What?

84
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,330
Master, Madam, Miss.

85
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:06,330
Go out and you'll see.

86
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,330
Why did you bring a rooster?

87
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:28,660
Where is General Weibei?

88
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:30,160
Our general is too busy.

89
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,030
According to etiquette,

90
00:05:31,030 --> 00:05:31,930
he used a rooster in his place

91
00:05:31,930 --> 00:05:33,530
to marry the Second Miss Wei.

92
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,860
Bastard!

93
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,230
I am his official wife.

94
00:05:36,330 --> 00:05:37,760
How could he be so perfunctory?

95
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,330
Today he promised personally

96
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:41,030
to marry Shen Luyi, the concubine, first

97
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:42,500
and then marry me grandly.

98
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,760
Our general keeps his word.

99
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:49,100
He specially ordered me to pick the biggest rooster

100
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:50,300
to come for the wedding.

101
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,260
Mother!

102
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:53,860
This is ridiculous.

103
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:58,790
It must be that bitch Shen Luyi who instigated it.

104
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,560
Remember,

105
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,820
His Majesty is inside.

106
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,960
In front of His Majesty and everyone,

107
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,960
we must get our dignity back.

108
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:16,960
Don't worry, Father.

109
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,260
Today, I will go all out

110
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:20,390
to ruin Shen Luyi's reputation

111
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:22,930
and make Lu Jingxing never look down on us again.
